solution:
```json
GET /sponsors/_search
{
  "query": {
    "bool": {
      "must": [
        { "match": { "description": "soda" } },
        { "match": { "description": "car" } },
        { "match": { "description": "shave" } }
      ],
      "must_not": [
        { "match": { "description": "beauty" } }
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

**Note:** each required word gets its own `must` clause (a single `match` defaults to OR internally across the words *within* one clause, so three separate `must` clauses are what enforces AND across all three words). The excluded word goes in `must_not`.
